Display timeline objects and rendering links in tweets

Then,  we need to make URLs in tweets clickable, and it works simply by adding the gem twitter-text-rb in gemfile

gem 'twitter-text'
Now, update application_helper.rb:

require 'twitter-text'
module ApplicationHelper
 
  include Twitter::Autolink
 
  def twitter_text(text)
    text = auto_link(text)
    text ? text.html_safe : ''
  end


Finally,  letâ€™s go to view and add this code:

<% @tweet_news.each do |tweet| %>
<ul>
    <li><%= twitter_text(tweet.text) %></li>
</ul>
<% end %>